metadata.title: stingray
metadata.visionDescription: The image depicts a cartoonish drawing of a person viewed from behind, with short brown hair, wearing a purple shirt. Surrounding the person are three abstract, curved shapes resembling the silhouettes of stingrays, in a gradient of dark to light blue. These shapes appear to float in a blue, circular, brushstroke-like background. The artwork has a simple, illustrative style with bold outlines and a limited color palette.

metadata.title: The Shard Norm
metadata.visionDescription: A humanoid figure stands against a cloudy, overcast sky. The character has a multicolored, iridescent face with prominent, curved horns and a long, pointed nose resembling an elephant's trunk. The figure is dressed in a dark, intricately detailed robe with a black and red color scheme, featuring gold accents. The robe has a high collar and is layered with armor-like elements, including circular emblems and an ornate pattern along the hem. The figure's arms are visible, showing skin with the same iridescent pattern as the face. The style is a blend of fantasy and science fiction, with a mysterious and otherworldly appearance.
